      <title>PTbox_Installation</title>
      <link href="/2024/10/15/PTbox-Installation/"/>
      <url>/2024/10/15/PTbox-Installation/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PT-box-安装教程"><a href="#PT-box-安装教程" class="headerlink" title="PT box 安装教程"></a>PT box 安装教程</h1><h2 id="dd-系统-与-开启-bbr"><a href="#dd-系统-与-开启-bbr" class="headerlink" title="dd 系统 与 开启 bbr"></a>dd 系统 与 开启 bbr</h2><p>略</p><h2 id="安装-SeedBox"><a href="#安装-SeedBox" class="headerlink" title="安装 SeedBox"></a>安装 SeedBox</h2><p>感谢项目作者  <a href="https://github.com/jerry048/Dedicated-Seedbox">jerry048&#x2F;Dedicated-Seedbox</a>  内有中文版本</p><p>更新源与安装必要依赖<br><code>apt-get update -y &amp;&amp; apt-get install -y curl wget sudo socat vim</code></p><p>安装Dedicated-Seedbox</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash &lt;(wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jerry048/Dedicated-Seedbox/main/Install.sh) -u jerry048 -p 1LDw39VOgors -c 6144 -q 4.3.9 -l v1.2.19 -b -v -r </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>命令详解</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. -u: 用户名                      jerry048</span><br><span class="line">2. -p: 密码                        1LDw39VOgors</span><br><span class="line">3. -c: qBitorrent 缓存             6144(6G，选用你内存的1/4)</span><br><span class="line">4. -q: qBittorrent 版本            4.3.9(版本不一定越新越好，4.3.x/4.5.x差不多)</span><br><span class="line">5. -l: libtorrent 版本             v1.2.19(qB不带v，这个有v，默认版本吧)</span><br><span class="line">6. -b: 安裝 autobrr                 刷外站神器</span><br><span class="line">7. -v: 安裝 vertex                  全方位追剧与流媒体管理工具</span><br><span class="line">8. -r: 安裝 autoremove-torrents     根据规则自动删除种子</span><br><span class="line">9. -3: 启动 BBR V3</span><br><span class="line">10.-x: 启动 BBRx</span><br><span class="line">11.-o: 自定义端口</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
