      <title>搭建nezha哪吒面板探针服务，监控你的所有VPS小鸡</title>
      <link href="/2024/10/14/nezha/"/>
      <url>/2024/10/14/nezha/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="搭建nezha哪吒面板探针服务"><a href="#搭建nezha哪吒面板探针服务" class="headerlink" title="搭建nezha哪吒面板探针服务"></a>搭建nezha哪吒面板探针服务</h1><h2 id="配置DNS"><a href="#配置DNS" class="headerlink" title="配置DNS"></a>配置DNS</h2><p>添加两个A记录，暂时都不开启CDN，一个用于部署网页服务(8080与443)，另一个作为接入节点<br>monitor暂时不打开cdn，等部署完成打开cdn，monitorcdn则永不打开cdn<br>A代表这是IPv4记录，AAAA就是v6，CNAME可以指向一个网址或者记录<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241014235145-9f0873db4639c07a406a7e46a6331e52.png"></p><h2 id="获取Github-OAuth认证"><a href="#获取Github-OAuth认证" class="headerlink" title="获取Github OAuth认证"></a>获取Github OAuth认证</h2><p>登录Github 右侧点击自己的头像打开导航栏  Settings -&gt; Developer Settings -&gt; OAuth Apps<br>或者访问 <a href="https://github.com/settings/developers">OAuth Apps</a>    然后点击右上角的 <code>New OAuth App</code></p><p>配置OAuth App，这里配置的是monitor，这个暂时不打开cdn，等部署完成就可以打开了<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241014235631-1a81b38d6fbbc3aeb03399d4c9691814.png"></p><p>别忘了点击下面的绿色按钮更新  <code>Update Application</code><br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241015000007-284ea51f21918dac978d6923f3059986.png"></p><h2 id="安装哪吒面板"><a href="#安装哪吒面板" class="headerlink" title="安装哪吒面板"></a>安装哪吒面板</h2><p>更新apt-get源，并通过apt-get下载所需软件与依赖<br><code>apt-get update -y &amp;&amp; apt-get install -y socat sudo wget vim curl</code></p><p>nezha安装脚本国外版本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -L https://raw.githubusercontent.com/naiba/nezha/master/script/install.sh  -o nezha.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x nezha.sh</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./nezha.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>选择 <code>2独立安装</code>，再选择 <code>1.  安装面板端</code><br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241015001149-d48d88685dd2907930275b66141d86be.png"></p><p>通过 ip:8008 来访问，可以访问则进入下一步<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241015012058-513d64969149470f1a3c076d1cdf942b.png"></p><h2 id="使用FreeSSL与Nginx反代"><a href="#使用FreeSSL与Nginx反代" class="headerlink" title="使用FreeSSL与Nginx反代"></a>使用FreeSSL与Nginx反代</h2><p>先在服务器上运行安装Amce.sh的脚本，直接全部复制粘贴运行，一般不会错</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl https://get.acme.sh | sh -s email=my@example.com</span><br><span class="line">cd /root/.acme.sh/</span><br><span class="line">alias acme.sh=~/.acme.sh/acme.sh</span><br><span class="line">acme.sh -h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://freessl.cn/chart">FreeSSL 控制台</a>  访问并注册或者登录</p><p>添加域名，进行SSL自动化<br>在最开始的记录是monitor，那么这里也需要是monitor，必须相同<br>这里是通过添加CNAME来验证<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241015234637-7e80c6bd286abd3c4ad5320c04393486.png"></p><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241015234958-9d7a1a07fda42625186bb666965a92f6.png"></p><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016000125-9e80537a4579911d38b04093cfe2b5ae.png"></p><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016000155-d8d5ae6cea212ce9003bd834ec234026.png"></p><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016000606-f63116a17c736d0f6f33def0a7863f38.png"></p><p>返回ssh连接<br>运行<code>cd /root/.acme.sh/</code><br>在运行上面复制下来的Acme.sh代码</p><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016001850-61adde8e41b54c2b1593bdbceed150ee.png"></p><p>安装nginx<br><code>apt-get install -y nginx</code><br>切换目录到&#x2F;etc&#x2F;nginx 这是nginx配置文件的所在地<br><code>cd /etc/nginx/</code></p><p>建议使用ssh工具的ftp工具来操作，以Termius为例，点击顶部的SFTP<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016010906-bebd8a12e3673e2b39b0a5c87e1acedd.png"></p><p>按照图片与之前Acme.sh的证书存储地进行配置<br><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016010705-bbe5c0cd7c40a3148964a6b0ce2111ea.png"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">user www-data;</span><br><span class="line">worker_processes auto;</span><br><span class="line">pid /run/nginx.pid;</span><br><span class="line">include /etc/nginx/modules-enabled/*.conf;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">events &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    worker_connections 768;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">http &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    include /etc/nginx/mime.types;</span><br><span class="line">    default_type application/octet-stream;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        listen 80;</span><br><span class="line">        listen 443 ssl http2;</span><br><span class="line">        server_name monitor.x.com;  ## 域名地址</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        index index.php index.html index.htm default.php default.htm default.html;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        ssl_certificate /root/xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx;  ## 公钥地址</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_certificate_key /root/xxxxxxxxxxx;  ## 私钥地址</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_ciphers &#x27;EECDH+AESGCM:EDH+AESGCM:AES256+EECDH:AES256+EDH&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m;</span><br><span class="line">        ssl_session_timeout 10m;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Strict-Transport-Security &quot;max-age=31536000&quot;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        error_page 497 https://$host$request_uri;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8008;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Host $http_host;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Connection &quot;Upgrade&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        location /ws &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8008;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_http_version 1.1;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Connection &quot;Upgrade&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">            proxy_set_header Host $http_host;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://img.myservps.work/2024-10/20241016011229-6a0171a494ccefeb2449bdc35a126393.png"></p><p>在SSH在输入<code>sudo nginx -t</code>验证配置是否正确，出现OK即为正确<br>再运行<code>sudo systemctl restart nginx</code>重启nginx服务</p><p>访问你的域名monitor.x.com能访问即为成功，到此完成</p>]]></content>
      
      
